== Create Vessel Type ==
Officer -> System : POST /api/vesseltype\nBody: CreatingVesselTypeDto(name, description, maxBays, maxRows, maxTiers)
System --> Officer : 201 Created\nBody: VesselTypeDto

== Update Vessel Type ==
Officer -> System : PUT /api/vesseltype/{id}\nBody: UpdateVesselTypeDto(name?, description?, maxBays?, maxRows?, maxTiers?)
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: VesselTypeDto (updated)\nOR 400 BadRequest

== Search Vessel Types ==
Officer -> System : GET /api/vesseltype/filter?name={name}&description={description}
System --> Officer : 200 OK\nBody: List<VesselTypeDto>\nOR 404 NotFound
